OL,3,CRoof collapses as fire tears through
OL,4,Cderelict building
OL,6,FCrews have spent the night tackling a
OL,7,Ffire at a derelict building in Gosport.
OL,9,FFirefighters from Gosport and
OL,10,FPortchester were called to Privett
OL,11,FRoad at 8pm on Wednesday (10 June)
OL,12,Fnight.
OL,14,FRoad closures were put in place on
OL,15,FPrivett Road, Privett Place and
OL,16,FDaniels Place due to the large amount
OL,17,Fof emergency service personnel in the
OL,18,Farea.
